title: Lavasan-e Bozorg
text: Lavasan-e Bozorg (, also <a href="Romanize">Romanize</a>d as Lavāsān-e Bozorg, Lavāsān Bozorg) is a village in <a href="Lavasan-e%20Bozorg%20Rural%20District">Lavasan-e Bozorg Rural District</a>, <a href="Lavasanat%20District">Lavasanat District</a>, <a href="Shemiranat%20County">Shemiranat County</a>, <a href="Tehran%20Province">Tehran Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>.
